headline: Independent Directors of Phillips 66 Issue Letter to Investors and Their Stewardship Teams
summary: HOUSTON, April 24, 2025--Phillips 66 sent a letter from the Independent Directors of the Board to the Company’s shareholders and to independent proxy advisors.
